{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Don't get me started on [? enchanted ?] subject, I-- we'll spend a-- we'll spend a week here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did the family--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, especially my dad because my mom had her own program.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm glad you asked that question because I was going to tell you about-- she-- first of all, my mom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had a program.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was called, in Polish, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Translated, it means wish-- the wishes-- the [? wishes ?] concert.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would play a song and this dedication-- with dedications.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Someone would call up, you know-- or you couldn't call up, but write into the station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is not like talk radio today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had, like, live shows, from a cabaret, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so those were her favorite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad loved a broadcast in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Yiddish broadcast came from the Russian and the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember when I would be doing my homework or try to read something, I would-- he would turn it up a little louder.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember the sound of the 'Internationale,' you know-- [HUMMING 'THE INTERNATIONALE'].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so here comes-- here comes a broadcast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it would come on, and my dad would be glued to that, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wants to crawl into that console.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the announcer would start out with a greeting of the typical proletarian greetings in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH] 'Unite.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Workers unite.' And my father was fascinated that there's a Yiddish program coming out of a Russian republic-- the USSR then.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course, what it was is propaganda, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because he was a coal miner, naturally, he would lean towards the workers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he would, you know, dream of a workers' paradise and quote some of the-- some of the ideology which he heard.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
